quran[15{c,v,t}:
15,91,jinhon ne apne quran ko tukre tukre kar dala hai
15,92,"tu qasam hai tairay Rab ki, hum zaroor un sab se poucheen ge"
15,93,ke tum kya karte rahay ho
15,94,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jis cheez ka tumhe hukum diya ja raha hai, ussay hankaypukare keh do aur shirk karne walon ki zara parwa nah karo"
15,95,tumhari taraf se hum unn mazaq urane walon ki khabar lainay ke liye kaafi hain
15,96,jo Allah ke sath kisi aur ko bhi khuda qarar dete hain anqareeb inhen maloom ho jaye ga
15,97,hamein maloom hai ke jo baatein yeh log tum par banatay hain un se tumahray dil ko sakht kofat hoti hai
15,98,"is ka ilaaj yeh hai ke apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo, is ki janab mein sajda baja lao"
15,99,aur uss aakhri gharri taq apne rab ki bandagi karte raho jis ka aana yakeeni hai
16,1,"aa gaya Allah ka faisla, ab is ke liye jaldi nah machao pak hai woh aur baala tar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log kar rahay hain"
16,2,"woh iss rooh ko apne jis bande par chahta hai apne hukum se mulaika ke zariye nazil farma deta hai ( iss hadaayat ke sath ke logon ko )"" aagah kar do, mere siwa koi tumhara mabood nahi hai, lehaza tum mujhi se daro """
16,3,"uss ne aasman o zameen ko brhq peda kya hai, woh bohat baala o bartar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
16,4,uss ne ensaan ko aik zara si boond se peda kya aur dekhte dekhte srihan woh aik jhagralu hasti ban gaya
16,5,"is ne janwar peda kiye jin mein tumahray liye poshak bhi hai aur khoraak bhi, aur terhan terhan ke dosray faiday bhi"
16,6,unn mein tumahray liye jamal hai jab ke subah tum inhen charnay ke liye bhaijtay ho aur jabkay shaam inhen wapas laatay ho
